des:
Carl Friedrich Gauss is considered to be the greatest mathematician to ever live. Some refer to him as "the Chuck Norris of Mathematics"... which is where Gauss jokes (or facts) originated. 

This simple skill gives you a Gauss Norris joke from a pool. Enjoy!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
